results.result: The top 10 customers based on total purchase amount have been successfully retrieved.
actions:
""
SELECT 
    c.customer_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.order_id) AS total_transactions,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) DESC) AS rank
FROM 
    customers c
JOIN 
    orders o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id
JOIN 
    order_items oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id
GROUP BY 
    c.customer_name
ORDER BY 
    SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) DESC
LIMIT 10
""

""
SELECT 
    (c.first_name || ' ' || c.last_name) AS customer_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.order_id) AS total_transactions,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) DESC) AS rank
FROM 
    customers c
JOIN 
    orders o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id
JOIN 
    order_items oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id
GROUP BY 
    c.customer_id
ORDER BY 
    SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) DESC
LIMIT 10
""

""
SELECT 
    (c.first_name || ' ' || c.last_name) AS customer_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.order_id) AS total_transactions,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SUM((oi.list_price - oi.discount) * oi.quantity) DESC) AS rank
FROM 
    customers c
JOIN 
    orders o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id
JOIN 
    order_items oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id
GROUP BY 
    c.customer_id
ORDER BY 
    SUM((oi.list_price - oi.discount) * oi.quantity) DESC
LIMIT 10
""
